Revision history for Perl script sopstream.

0.1.0  Tue Apr 26 13:00:00 2011
    - Restructured single script into 2 embedded modules to simplify testing.
    - Moved sopcast client kill command into a separate module.
    - Added local caching of channel list (to reduce number of times needed to fetch from website)
    - Added in-memory caching of channel list (to reduce multiple file accesses of channel list)

0.0.1  Tue Apr 26 12:30:00 2011
	- First proper project structure with makefile etc.
	- Supports playing sopcast stream by URL, name, channel number.
	- Each invocation by name/search will consult a website to retrieve the 
	  channel name/number mapping.

